In the years since Hurricane Sandy damaged much of the subway system, the city has committed to devising solutions to help stem the rising tides caused by global warming—including a tampon-like device called a “tunnel plug.” Here are some other ideas, in Fantasy Island, Subway edition, by Luci Gutiérrez.

Here they are, your favorite New Yorker cartoons of 2019, ranked by number of likes. They include new cartoons and old cartoons, jokes about work and weddings, plenty of cats and dogs, and one rather heartfelt portrait of our hero, Greta Thunberg. Tap the link in the bio to see them all.
